    gameDate,  -- The date of the game
    HOME,      -- The home team

datasets.name: e60fe859
datasets.query:
SELECT 
    a.gameDate,
    a.gameId,
    a.shooterName,
    a.playerTeam,
    a.opposingTeam,
    a.season,
    a.absVarianceAvgLast7SOG,
    ROUND(a.predictedSOG, 2) AS predictedSOG,
    a.`SOG_2+`, 
    a.`SOG_3+`, 
    a.`player_2+_SeasonHitRate`, 
    a.`player_3+_SeasonHitRate`, 
    a.`player_2+_SeasonMatchupHitRate`, 
    a.`player_3+_SeasonMatchupHitRate`, 
    a.previous_opposingTeam, 
    a.previous_player_Total_goals, 
    a.previous_player_Total_shotsOnGoal, 
    a.previous_player_Total_shotAttempts,
    a.playerGamesPlayedRolling,
    a.player_total_shotsOnGoal AS playerSOG,
    a.previous_player_Total_shotsOnGoal AS playerLastSOG,
    a.average_player_Total_shotsOnGoal_last_3_games AS playerAvgSOGLast3,
    a.average_player_Total_shotsOnGoal_last_7_games AS playerAvgSOGLast7,
    a.previous_player_Total_iceTimeRank AS playerIceTimeRank,
    a.previous_player_PP_iceTimeRank AS playerPPIceTimeRank,
    a.previous_player_Total_shotAttempts AS playerShotAtt,
    a.previous_perc_rank_rolling_game_Total_goalsFor AS `teamGoalsForRank%`,
    a.previous_perc_rank_rolling_game_Total_shotsOnGoalFor AS `teamSOGForRank%`,
    a.previous_perc_rank_rolling_game_PP_SOGForPerPenalty AS `teamPPSOGRank%`,
    a.opponent_previous_rolling_per_game_Total_shotsOnGoalAgainst AS `oppSOGAgainst`,
    a.opponent_previous_perc_rank_rolling_game_Total_goalsAgainst AS `oppGoalsAgainstRank%`,
    a.opponent_previous_perc_rank_rolling_game_Total_shotsOnGoalAgainst AS `oppSOGAgainstRank%`,
    a.opponent_previous_perc_rank_rolling_game_Total_penaltiesFor AS `oppPenaltiesRank%`,
    a.opponent_previous_perc_rank_rolling_game_PK_SOGAgainstPerPenalty AS `oppPKSOGRank%`,
    a.`average_player_SOG%_PP_last_7_games` AS `playerLast7PPSOG%`,
    a.`average_player_SOG%_EV_last_7_games` AS `playerLast7EVSOG%`,
    a.previous_perc_rank_rolling_player_Total_goals AS `playerGoalsForRank%`,
    a.previous_perc_rank_rolling_player_Total_shotAttempts AS `playerShotAttRank%`,
    a.previous_perc_rank_rolling_player_Total_ShotsOnGoal AS `playerSOGRank%`,
    a.previous_perc_rank_rolling_player_PP_SOGAttemptsForPerPenalty AS `playerPPShotAttRank%`,
    a.previous_perc_rank_rolling_player_PP_SOGPerPenalty AS `playerPPSOGRank%`,
    a.previous_perc_rank_rolling_player_PP_goalsPerPenalty AS `playerPPGoalsRank%`,
    a.is_within_30_days,
    a.is_last_played_game,
    a.is_last_played_game_team,
    a.latestMatchupCounter,
    a.latestMatchupFlag,
    b.Explanation,
    g.AWAY,
    away_team.name AS away_team_name,
    away_team.`venue/city` AS away_venue_city,
    g.HOME,
    home_team.name AS home_team_name,
    home_team.`venue/city` AS home_venue_city,
    g.sum_game_Total_goalsFor,
    g.sum_game_Total_goalsAgainst,
    g.isWin
FROM lr_nhl_demo.dev.clean_prediction_v2 a
LEFT JOIN lr_nhl_demo.dev.llm_summary b
    ON a.shooterName = b.shooterName AND a.gameId IS NULL
LEFT JOIN lr_nhl_demo.dev.gold_game_stats_clean g
    ON a.gameId = g.gameId AND a.playerTeam = g.playerTeam
LEFT JOIN lr_nhl_demo.dev.team_code_mappings away_team 
    ON g.AWAY = away_team.abbreviation
LEFT JOIN lr_nhl_demo.dev.team_code_mappings home_team 
    ON g.HOME = home_team.abbreviation
WHERE a.season = 2024
ORDER BY a.gameDate DESC, a.predictedSOG DESC;

    a.playerTeam,
    a.opposingTeam,

    a.previous_perc_rank_rolling_game_PP_SOGForPerPenalty AS `teamPPSOGRank%`,
    a.opponent_previous_rolling_per_game_Total_shotsOnGoalAgainst AS oppSOGAgainstPerGame,
    a.opponent_previous_perc_rank_rolling_game_Total_goalsAgainst AS `oppGoalsAgainstRank%`,
    a.opponent_previous_perc_rank_rolling_game_Total_shotsOnGoalAgainst AS `oppSOGAgainstRank%`,
    a.opponent_previous_perc_rank_rolling_game_Total_penaltiesFor AS `oppPenaltiesRank%`,
    a.opponent_previous_rolling_game_PK_SOGAgainstPerPenalty AS `oppPKSOGRank%`,
    a.`average_player_SOG%_PP_last_7_games` AS `playerLast7PPSOG%`,
    a.`average_player_SOG%_EV_last_7_games` AS `playerLast7EVSOG%`,
    a.previous_perc_rank_rolling_player_Total_goals AS `playerGoalsForRank%`,
    a.previous_perc_rank_rolling_player_Total_shotAttempts AS `playerShotAttRank%`,
    a.previous_perc_rank_rolling_player_Total_ShotsOnGoal AS `playerSOGRank%`,
    a.previous_perc_rank_rolling_player_PP_SOGAttemptsForPerPenalty AS `playerPPShotAttRank%`,
    a.previous_perc_rank_rolling_player_PP_SOGPerPenalty AS `playerPPSOGRank%`,
    a.previous_perc_rank_rolling_player_PP_goalsPerPenalty AS `playerPPGoalsRank%`,
    a.is_last_played_game,
    a.is_last_played_game_team,
    b.Explanation
FROM lr_nhl_demo.dev.clean_prediction_v2 a
LEFT JOIN lr_nhl_demo.dev.llm_summary b
ON a.shooterName = b.shooterName AND a.gameId IS NULL
WHERE a.gameId IS NULL
ORDER BY a.gameDate ASC, a.predictedSOG DESC, a.absVarianceAvgLast7SOG DESC;

datasets.query:
SELECT 
    gameDate,
    shooterName,
    playerTeam,
    opposingTeam,
    season,
    absVarianceAvgLast7SOG,
    ROUND(predictedSOG, 2) AS predictedSOG,
    -- player_total_shotsOnGoal AS playerSOG,
    `average_player_SOG%_PP_last_7_games` AS `playerLast7PPSOG%`,
    `average_player_SOG%_EV_last_7_games` AS `playerLast7EVSOG%`,
    previous_player_Total_shotsOnGoal AS playerLastSOG,
    average_player_Total_shotsOnGoal_last_3_games AS playerAvgSOGLast3,
    average_player_Total_shotsOnGoal_last_7_games AS playerAvgSOGLast7,
    previous_perc_rank_rolling_player_Total_goals AS `playerGoalsForRank%`,
    previous_perc_rank_rolling_player_Total_shotAttempts AS `playerShotAttRank%`,
    previous_perc_rank_rolling_player_Total_ShotsOnGoal AS `playerSOGRank%`,
    previous_perc_rank_rolling_player_PP_SOGAttemptsForPerPenalty AS `playerPPShotAttRank%`,
    previous_perc_rank_rolling_player_PP_SOGPerPenalty AS `playerPPSOGRank%`,
    previous_perc_rank_rolling_player_PP_goalsPerPenalty AS `playerPPGoalsRank%`
FROM lr_nhl_demo.dev.clean_prediction_v2
WHERE gameId IS NULL
ORDER BY gameDate ASC, absVarianceAvgLast7SOG DESC, predictedSOG DESC;
